'''SRES'''

# [[w:Special report on emissions scenarios|Special report on emissions scenarios]]
# '''S'''igned '''RES'''ponse to authentication challenge. A term used in GSM mobile networks. The network sends a challenge to the mobile at each connection, and the mobile must send a SRES back to the network before it will allow access. 

